{"tid":2397300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"怒轟「林鄭食屎」瞓花槽被抬走  馬鞍山街坊衝閘：我要返工","createTime":"2021-02-06T10:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T15:47:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"269e59f9eb0de39745e93d15b4cf9061623a33a4","tid":2397300,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/WNEZLLHHKVGJLN2FR7GJ7V5F4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2FWNEZLLHHKVGJLN2FR7GJ7V5F4U%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=71e328cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2FWNEZLLHHKVGJLN2FR7GJ7V5F4U%2F&h=54b9cb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/WNEZLLHHKVGJLN2FR7GJ7V5F4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n怒轟「林鄭食屎」瞓花槽被抬走 <br />\n馬鞍山街坊衝閘：我要返工<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】揚言封區檢測封到年廿九的特區政府懶理居民反對，連續第六晚「突閘」，昨晚封鎖馬鞍山恒安邨恒江樓與元朗富來花園，有恒安邨居民不滿大廈納強檢，一家大小剛完成檢測，未料再被「禁足」強檢，怒不可遏鬧爆「林鄭食屎啦！」晚上更有男女街坊企圖突破封鎖線衝閘失敗被警員制服，反映離地又擾民的封區政策已激起民憤。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：商務免檢 深圳男抵港確診  反列本地個案 所住映灣園現六個案<br />\n<br />\n昨晚7時04分，當局宣佈圍封元。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n消息公佈之前，大批警員和民政處人員已經到達兩處地點，除有物資車輛到達，亦有工作人員設立檢測站，警員更圍起封鎖區驅趕記者。有恒江樓居民向樓下大叫「好擾民呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4XQQdO_u5QMg21N-m0q6ACCxROc=/808x1952/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HTGIQVHYSZBNTFGRVWEBGCVOV4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4XQQdO_u5QMg21N-m0q6ACCxROc%3D%2F808x1952%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHTGIQVHYSZBNTFGRVWEBGCVOV4.gif&h=737b41c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全家昨午採樣 晚上再檢測<br />\n<br />\n至晚上8時許，陸續有身穿全副防護衣的警員上樓拍門通知居民檢測，其間新界南總區指揮官麥展豪身穿便服到場視察。不少居民不滿被禁足，街坊盧先生表現勞氣，任職運輸業的他向記者展示已接受檢測的短訊，指大廈剛於周四被納入強檢，自己一家大小昨午才前往社區中心採樣站完成檢測，未料晚飯後下樓購物回來才知大廈被封，又要再做強檢。<br />\n<br />\n盧先生向樓下警員多次詢問，對方答稱需要再做令他不滿，「佢話『你快啲返上樓啦，如果唔係我哋要捉人』咁樣」。<br />\n<br />\n他直斥封區無需要且重複，造成混亂，又指自己從事運輸業，未能5時出門上班，狠斥「林鄭食屎啦」、「成班民建聯垃圾，無咗民主黨就係呢班垃圾」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中年男：我都有我嘅自由<br />\n<br />\n其後居民劉先生亦大吐苦水，指前日大廈被納入強檢，何不同日封鎖大廈，不明政府做法。任職的士司機的他每早清晨5時開工，今早勢不能開工，昨晚已通知老闆遲開工。<br />\n<br />\n當局亂封區早引起居民不滿，昨晚10時許，有中年男住客在恒江樓與警員發生理論，其間男住客突然情緒激動，擺脫警員往封鎖線方向衝去，警員隨即追上將他截停，現場所見該男子不斷掙扎，又大喊「我都有我嘅自由」，最後遭警員帶往帳篷安撫情緒，暫未知會否被捕。<br />\n<br />\n一小時後，另一名穿粉紅色上衣中年女子落樓打算離開，並與在場警員和海關關員爭執。其間她情緒激動，警員勸止無效一度拉扯，最後該女子卧在臨時檢測站附近花槽，用手死死抓住欄杆不放。在場警員和民政處人員一直在旁勸解，並講解法例要求。然而她仍然激動，不斷說「我之前咪檢測咗囉」、「我要返工呀」，最終擾攘15分鐘後被警員抬離花槽。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。有居民鬧爆當局每晚行動勞民傷財，直言：「攞啲資源派畀巿民仲好！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CJjB4Dr0O3p8b3o8q2_SJwFqcS4=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YZBKVEAQJZFDRK3CLSHAXAMDUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCJjB4Dr0O3p8b3o8q2_SJwFqcS4%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYZBKVEAQJZFDRK3CLSHAXAMDUE.jpg&h=44f7a185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【馬鞍山】■一名中年男住客衝往封鎖線被警員截停，男住客大喊「我都有我嘅自由！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gZswWqAwlNPb1Fh4L4QjNq7MqYg=/1051x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CEUMXUW7TJF7LMK7FWTIN6VCAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgZswWqAwlNPb1Fh4L4QjNq7MqYg%3D%2F1051x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCEUMXUW7TJF7LMK7FWTIN6VCAI.jpg&h=54aa3905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街坊盧先生預料今早未能在5時出門上班，狠斥「林鄭食屎啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bjN2Yi56yoMiPXQVT8X7vxaXn1M=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YOXADGWUJJEU7DYQT3FGOSDAWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbjN2Yi56yoMiPXQVT8X7vxaXn1M%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYOXADGWUJJEU7DYQT3FGOSDAWA.jpg&h=62e59be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■納入強檢的馬鞍山恒安邨恒江樓，昨晚突遭圍封。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WWMXKVgl3mUU7vDw6DiSxxsqfko=/591x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L6H7X6JY2JASVBP5PHSRMG5ZFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWWMXKVgl3mUU7vDw6DiSxxsqfko%3D%2F591x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL6H7X6JY2JASVBP5PHSRMG5ZFI.jpg&h=c00f054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【元 朗】■元朗富來花園A、B兩座列受限區域，所有住戶須接受強檢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8lb_cy-L-i20jmXoJOLhlHb5-Dg=/369x421/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2ASKBSCQ55GL5MFJS2IMZIH72Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8lb_cy-L-i20jmXoJOLhlHb5-Dg%3D%2F369x421%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2ASKBSCQ55GL5MFJS2IMZIH72Y.gif&h=88c6e77f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05538cb54b47eb101f611d86cdaf08f0481d3b67","tid":2397300,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"黎氏上班撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66da6256fe9e74c1f127129e12f9d5dad48470fe","tid":2397300,"uid":282347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"黎氏家族咁多成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b710998ca5f88968b382fdb2a510d56970f77eb2","tid":2397300,"uid":146621,"like":1,"disli